    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable under the MRL 2 requirements for a Class II CPB device. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to support the intended decision of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and comparing against the predicate device using the RH < 1 acceptance criterion.",
